<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This trigger event is sent by the placer application to the filler application to request anti-microbial device cycle data created during the decontamination/sterilization of medical supplies. In the context of this message segment, the term 'device' refers to a sterilizer or a washer. Sterilizers perform a sterilization process and washers perform a decontamination process.</p>
</div>
